---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About">
  <section class="section">
    <h2>About TableTopLearning</h2>
    <p>TableTopLearning is a warm, modern and education-focused brand that combines approachable design with trusted learning support.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <h3>Brand personality</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Friendly</li>
      <li>Encouraging</li>
      <li>Professional</li>
      <li>Practical</li>
      <li>Modern</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <h3>Design direction</h3>
    <p>We use warm, soft gradients, rounded cards and a calm layout to keep the experience clear, premium and easy to use.</p>
    <p>Our copy is clear, encouraging and learner-focused: build skills step by step with the right support at the right time.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <h3>Core brand colours</h3>
    <p>Primary accent: <strong>#bd5500</strong>, supporting background: <strong>#fff8ec</strong>, surface card: <strong>#ffffff</strong> and text: <strong>#594a40</strong>.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <h3>Logo direction</h3>
    <p>Use a simple text-based wordmark that is clear and readable. Keep the TTL icon visible but unobtrusive.</p>
  </section>
</Layout>
